  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099580/extras/fe9ec6e08b64fe58d31f952d0afc404e.poster.avif?t=1750476050\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099580/extras/fe9ec6e08b64fe58d31f952d0afc404e.webm?t=1750476050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099580/extras/fe9ec6e08b64fe58d31f952d0afc404e.mp4?t=1750476050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099580/extras/fa9250b038ca7534557f5d40e5e1cf81.webp?t=1750476050\" width=200 height=34 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The main character stands on the brink of despair, having lost someone dear to him. In an attempt to cope with the loss and find meaning in life, he encounters a mysterious stranger. This enigmatic figure offers him an unusual path to healing—a journey into the depths of his own mind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As he dives into his consciousness, the hero discovers that familiar places from his past have turned into distorted realms, where every corner is filled with nightmares. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099580/extras/4bd667224e009bcf79313b07b6e17e2e.avif?t=1750476050\" width=600 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099580/extras/4e8eaccb785bb84111e7f0d06f8c1d4a.poster.avif?t=1750476050\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099580/extras/4e8eaccb785bb84111e7f0d06f8c1d4a.webm?t=1750476050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099580/extras/4e8eaccb785bb84111e7f0d06f8c1d4a.mp4?t=1750476050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099580/extras/261fd842b34d262f8b5f2264154e875e.webp?t=1750476050\" width=200 height=34 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game offers a blend of psychological horror and exploration. Terrifying creatures lurk around every corner, each one embodying the protagonist’s deepest fears. Explore a variety of distorted locations drawn from his memories, solve puzzles, and uncover long-buried secrets from the past.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throughout the journey, you'll face a range of enemies, each representing a specific aspect of the protagonist’s trauma and inner struggles. Atmospheric sound design, immersive audio, and haunting music work together to create a deeply engaging experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099580/extras/4bd667224e009bcf79313b07b6e17e2e.avif?t=1750476050\" width=600 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099580/extras/a5ecf6e2f57eaddf791cdc0b27c590b7.webp?t=1750476050\" width=200 height=34 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The protagonist must navigate the dark landscapes of their mind, uncovering the secrets of their subconscious and facing demons long hidden in the shadows. The journey will be not only a struggle to save a friend but also a quest for the true self.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099580/extras/7dcf41bbfabc7e3c04d768bcb863567e.avif?t=1750476050\" width=600 height=229 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099580/extras/4bd667224e009bcf79313b07b6e17e2e.avif?t=1750476050\" width=600 height=70 /></span></p>",
